window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They say revenge is a dish best served cold...<br> <br> But I'd rather serve it hot, with a side of humiliation.</b><br> <br> The Icons got what they wanted. My life is a smoldering wreck because of them.<br> <br> But that doesn't mean I'm done fighting.<br> <br> What I did to Trent is just the beginning. He deserves so much worse for what he's done to me.<br> <br> West and Reese are no better. They told me they cared about me, but when it mattered most, they took his side over mine.<br> <br> My body still craves all of them.<br> <br> But my broken heart?<br> <br> It just wants to take all of them down.</p> <p><i>This is book two of the Clearwater University series, a new adult reverse harem enemies to lovers romance. It contains cursing and steam.</i></p>"; 
